<span id="freeTextContainer9473462141177748609">Lisa See is a Chinese-American author. Her books include <i>Snow Flower and the Secret Fan</i> (2005), <i>Dragon Bones</i>, and <i>On Gold Mountain</i>. She was named the 2001 National Woman of the Year, by the Organization of Chinese American Women. She lives in Los Angeles.<br/><br/></span>

